{"tid":1267645,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約車站閃現「G20撐港」","createTime":"2019-06-30T03:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T03:52:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ca75be55791f4d68c7bd487254c5fa596eca0d42","tid":1267645,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:57:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190630/20716823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F20716823&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGhBk8ry%2Bv12G5j1RUyKX8i0%3D&h=2829d368\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F20716823&h=c418f29c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190630/20716823</a><br />\n<br />\n紐約車站閃現「G20撐港」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190630/large/30la7p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190630%2Flarge%2F30la7p5.jpg&h=3bdc78a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逾150名港人在紐約中央車站高舉《紐約時報》聲援香港。鄭柏齡攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港人並不孤單，撤回《逃犯條例》修訂訴求響徹全球。在紐約中央車站，當地時間周五晚上，一名黑衣人站在大堂上閱讀《紐約時報》，報章上有一個全版廣告：「Stand with Hong Kong at G20（G20與香港並肩）」。<br />\n<br />\n然後，越來越多人打開《紐約時報》站着不動，10個、20個、150個&hellip;&hellip;持續最少十分鐘。這是網民號召的快閃行動，召集人稱自周一以來，世界各地港人已籌集逾670萬元購買主要國際報紙的空間，表達對引渡法案的反對意見，為發揮行動影響力，讓港人聲音可響徹紐約，故在中央車站舉辦行動。<br />\n<br />\n有關組織計劃去信紐約州、新澤西州、康州全數6位參議員及44位眾議員，促請他們維護香港自由和民主，籲各界聯署。除紐約，加拿大溫哥華亦在當地時間今日中午舉行同樣行動。<br />\n<br />\n■記者羅佩琼  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n稱「太多暴動」的總撐林鄭<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n移民20年6月投身抗爭路 澳洲女護7.1與港人同行"},{"pid":"b57485226b731c92216593f4eef6f07bb27e2fbd","tid":1267645,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f86af41baa791e26d54d71eae4ed1ec0d6ccd25","tid":1267645,"uid":65196,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:11:26.000Z","msg":"多謝巴絲打"},{"pid":"f5a1941a9afbb7358c9b83a965fdfb652930704b","tid":1267645,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1fe0ff2ec6a5d2cac0e5398a3ccae47b2d4f7c4","tid":1267645,"uid":54228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yn7ASQz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYn7ASQz.jpg&h=551baa69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad37c2b64d4c9824c88e36e015b2b6160380cd2a","tid":1267645,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123b6302fe3bbfa54b7d64076d0d73c298b04f01","tid":1267645,"uid":194920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:52:35.000Z","msg":"我係嗰度呀，得我一個九十後"}]}